headline: Copart, Inc. to Release First Quarter Fiscal 2025 Results
summary: DALLAS, November 12, 2024--Copart, Inc. (NASDAQ: CPRT) announced today that it will release earnings for the first quarter of fiscal 2025 after 4:00 p.m. Eastern Time (3:00 p.m. Central) on Thursday, November 21, 2024.
